      <item>
        <title>coder server搭建</title>
        <description>
&lt;h2 id=&quot;搭建&quot;&gt;搭建&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;通过docker镜像来快速搭建&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-docker highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;  docker run -d --name code-server -p 8070:8080 \
  -v &quot;$PWD/.config:/home/coder/.config&quot; \
  -v &quot;$PWD/code-server:/home/coder/project&quot; \
  -u &quot;$(id -u):$(id -g)&quot; \
  -e &quot;DOCKER_USER=$USER&quot; \
  codercom/code-server:latest
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
